      <li>
        <h5>How is Git different from SVN?</h5>
        <p>The most significant difference is that Git is decentralized, while SVN is not. See <a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/871" target="_blank">StackOverflow: Why is Git better than Subversion?</a>.</p>
